        "Click 'Sync Now' to trigger an immediate sync",
        "Check the 'Queue Statistics' section to see pending/synced/failed counts",
        "View 'Recent Sessions' to see the history of sync operations",
        "Use the 'Queue Items' viewer to filter and inspect individual sync items",
        "Click 'Retry Failed' to re-queue any items that previously failed",
        "Click 'Clear Synced' to remove old completed items from the queue (older than 7 days)"
