      "troubleshooting_items": [
        "If 'Test Connection' fails: double-check your Supabase URL and keys — make sure there are no extra spaces",
        "If sync items are failing: check the error messages in the queue viewer for details",
        "If stuck in 'syncing' state: restart the app to reset the sync loop",
        "If tables are missing: run the SQL migration script again in the Supabase SQL Editor",
        "If RLS errors appear: ensure the migration script was run completely (it sets up row-level security policies)",
        "If you change your Supabase password: you don't need to reconfigure — the service_role key doesn't change",
